{"tha-ap20:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap20:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap20:0.3":"Ratthapalattheraapadana ","tha-ap20:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap20:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap20:1.3":"Varanago maya dinno, ","tha-ap20:1.4":"Isadanto urulhava. ","tha-ap20:2.1":"Setacchatto pasobhito, ","tha-ap20:2.2":"sakappano sahatthipo; ","tha-ap20:2.3":"Agghapetvana tam sabbam, ","tha-ap20:2.4":"sangharamam akarayim. ","tha-ap20:3.1":"Catupannasasahassani, ","tha-ap20:3.2":"pasade karayim aham; ","tha-ap20:3.3":"Mahoghadanam karitvana, ","tha-ap20:3.4":"niyyadesim mahesino. ","tha-ap20:4.1":"Anumodi mahaviro, ","tha-ap20:4.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap20:4.3":"Sabbe jane hasayanto, ","tha-ap20:4.4":"desesi amatam padam. ","tha-ap20:5.1":"Tam me buddho viyakasi, ","tha-ap20:5.2":"jalajuttaranamako; ","tha-ap20:5.3":"Bhikkhusanghe nisiditva, ","tha-ap20:5.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap20:6.1":"‘Catupannasasahassani, ","tha-ap20:6.2":"pasade karayi ayam; ","tha-ap20:6.3":"Kathayissami vipakam, ","tha-ap20:6.4":"sunotha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap20:7.1":"Attharasasahassani, ","tha-ap20:7.2":"kutagara bhavissare; ","tha-ap20:7.3":"Byamhuttamamhi nibbatta, ","tha-ap20:7.4":"sabbasonnamaya ca te. ","tha-ap20:8.1":"Pannasakkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap20:8.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap20:8.3":"Atthapannasakkhattunca, ","tha-ap20:8.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap20:9.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap20:9.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap20:9.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap20:9.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap20:10.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap20:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap20:10.3":"Addhe kule mahabhoge, ","tha-ap20:10.4":"nibbattissati tavade. ","tha-ap20:11.1":"So paccha pabbajitvana, ","tha-ap20:11.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap20:11.3":"Ratthapaloti namena, ","tha-ap20:11.4":"hessati satthu savako. ","tha-ap20:12.1":"Padhanapahitatto so, ","tha-ap20:12.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap20:12.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap20:12.4":"nibbayissatinasavo’. ","tha-ap20:13.1":"Utthaya abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap20:13.2":"jahita bhogasampada; ","tha-ap20:13.3":"Khelapindeva bhogamhi, ","tha-ap20:13.4":"pemam mayham na vijjati. ","tha-ap20:14.1":"Viriyam me dhuradhorayham, ","tha-ap20:14.2":"yogakkhemadhivahanam; ","tha-ap20:14.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap20:14.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap20:15.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap20:15.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap20:15.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap20:15.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap20:16.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ratthapalo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap20:17.1":"Ratthapalattherassapadanam atthamam. "}